metadata.name: The Punisher Birth
metadata.description:
"The Birth of the body is not the the Birth of the Soul, energy is eternal. Two sides on singularity, empty but full. Here. The transformation begins, punish the punisher Move, carry the cross, going, whatever it takes, break free. Here"

Cris Vond
